{"tid":1607701,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【香城online】狗種分析","createTime":"2019-10-01T03:03:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T03:32:05.000Z","uid":37528,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1369152c1634e4507a59724d52ef85580f4b80dd","tid":1607701,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:03:57.000Z","msg":"<ins><strong>畜龍</strong></ins><br />\n速度高，攻擊力強，有楜椒球槍(唔知有無實彈槍)<br />\n專長：<br />\n1. 鬼鬼鼠鼠咁從後扯人袋拉跌人同埋推跌人，再幾隻狗擒一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.  我地人多時，佢地會保持距離對我地開槍<br />\n弱點：<br />\n1. 防守力好低(所以先跑得快)<br />\n2. 佢地人數通常少，同埋好散。當我地夠人時，佢地好撚細膽會掉頭走<br />\n應對：<br />\n一定唔可以背著畜龍走。上次夏慤就係班畜龍衝過黎，我地背著走，但係前面又塞著好多人，所以先咁多手足俾畜龍捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>防暴</strong></ins><br />\n有盾有棍有gear重裝<br />\n專長：<br />\n1. full gear防守力強<br />\n2. 通常人數會較多向前推進<br />\n3. 不斷用棍打盾嚇9人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n弱點：<br />\n1. 相對上較慢同論盡，如果我地有位跑既話可以散到<br />\n2. 咁重gear，焗到佢地仆街，氣力bar會低d(成日見佢地隨頭盔抹汗)<br />\n<br />\n總結：<br />\n見到畜龍千其唔好背對著佢地跑，但前線一定要有盾<br />\n仲有要小心水炮車，應該未開盡全力射人，唔可以鬆懈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b4ee897fbdf87c8c325e393a36b43afc9dc0a72","tid":1607701,"uid":144084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bnUOGy9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbnUOGy9.png&h=ea09c098&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n捉鬼大綱上線<br />\n一發現有鬼第一時間唔係打... <br />\n而係...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1604858\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1604858</a><br />\n幫手推到前線有共識 !!!"},{"pid":"6911593d6a1e34a8616bfc3a384635737052e6d9","tid":1607701,"uid":37528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:30:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0aa36492d436ce65be2007b7dc99f1fb1ba2ec79","tid":1607701,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T03:32:05.000Z","msg":"畜龍都有實彈。注意。"}]}